commit_message_format.template:
fix: upgrade {package} to {version} for CVE-{ID}

- Addresses CVE-{ID} in {package}
- Upgraded from {old-version} to {new-version}
- Concert recommendation: {recommendation-details}
- Resolves #{issue-number}

transitive_dependency_documentation.format:
Add to "📝 Additional Notes" section:

**Transitive Dependency Considerations:**
- {List any transitive dependencies affected}
- {Note any version conflicts discovered during pip install verification}
- {Mention if additional package updates may be needed}
- {Reference pip install --dry-run results if relevant}

completion_message_format.template:
✅ CVE remediation complete:
- Created PR #{pr_number}: {pr_title}
- PR URL: {html_url}
- Branch: {branch_name}
- Package: {package} upgraded from {old_version} to {new_version}
- Resolves issue #{issue_number}
